<div class="create-feedback">
	<div class="feedback-container">
		<p>Contact us!</p>
		<h3> The SportsVenue&trade; team believes strongly in unmatchable high standards when it comes to product develpoment. And so, we always crave for user's feedback so that we can improve ourselves and take SportsVenue&trade; to another level.</h3>
		<!-- <form action="/create" method="POST" id="crtGrnd"> -->
		<div id="feedbackForm">
			<div class="inputs">
				<label for="uName">Your name</label>
				<input type="text" size="30" placeholder="Your name" id="uName" required></input>
			</div>
			<div class="inputs">
				<label for="uEmail">Your email-id</label>
				<input type="text" size="30" placeholder="Your Email id" id="uEmail" required></input>
			</div>
			<div class="inputs">
				<label for="uSubject">Subject of feedback/complaint - </label>
				<input type="text" size="30" placeholder="Subject" id="uSubject" required></input>
			</div>
			<div class="inputs">
				<label for="uInfo">Detailed feedback/complaint - </label>
				<div>
					<textarea placeholder="Your feedback/complaint" id="uInfo" rows="4" required></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="inputs">
				<label for="uNum">Your contact number - </label>
				<input type="text" placeholder="Contact number" id="uNum" required></input>
			</div>
			<div class="submit-section">
				<input type="submit" value="Send your feedback/complaint" class="search-button" id="sendFeedback"/>
				<input type="reset" value="Clear all" class="search-button"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="resp-success hide">
			<p>Thank you for your response!</p>
			<h3>Thank you for showing interest in us. Your response is sent to the administrator successfully. SportsVenue&trade; team will make sure that action is taken appropriately based on your response!</h3>
			<div class="button-section">
					<a href="/contact_us" id="createNew">Another feedback?!</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
